Default values:

---------------------
Before the simulation loop (t = 0):
---------------------
 1: S1 ~ N1 - E1 - A1 - R1 - C1 - H1 - I1 - D1
 2: V2 ~ N2 - E2 - A2 - R2 - C2 - H2 - I2 - D2
 3: V3 ~ N3 - E3 - A3 - R3 - C3 - H3 - I3 - D3
 4: S ~ S1 + V2 + V3
 5: E ~ E1 + E2 + E3
 6: A ~ A1 + A2 + A3
 7: R ~ R1 + R2 + R3
 8: C ~ C1 + C2 + C3
 9: H ~ H1 + H2 + H3
10: I ~ I1 + I2 + I3
11: D ~ D1 + D2 + D3
12: N ~ N1 + N2 + N3

---------------------
At every iteration of the simulation loop (t = 1 to T):
---------------------
 1: mp_per_capita_flow(from = "S1", to = "E1", rate = foi1 ~ kappa1 * 
      beta * (tau * I + zeta * A)/N)
 2: mp_per_capita_flow(from = "E1", to = "I1", rate = infect_symp1 ~ 
      sigma * mu)
 3: mp_per_capita_flow(from = "E1", to = "A1", rate = infect_asymp1 ~ 
      sigma * (1 - mu))
 4: mp_per_capita_flow(from = "A1", to = "R1", rate = asymp_recov1 ~ 
      gamma)
 5: mp_per_capita_flow(from = "I1", to = "H1", rate = symp_hosp1 ~ 
      phi1 * xi1)
 6: mp_per_capita_flow(from = "I1", to = "R1", rate = symp_recov1 ~ 
      phi1 * (1 - xi1))
 7: mp_per_capita_flow(from = "H1", to = "R1", rate = hosp_recov1 ~ 
      omega1 * (1 - theta1))
 8: mp_per_capita_flow(from = "H1", to = "C1", rate = hosp_icu1 ~ 
      omega1 * theta1)
 9: mp_per_capita_flow(from = "C1", to = "R1", rate = icu_recov1 ~ 
      eta1 * (1 - lambda1))
10: mp_per_capita_flow(from = "C1", to = "D1", rate = icu_dead1 ~ 
      eta1 * lambda1)
11: mp_per_capita_flow(from = "S1", to = "V2", rate = s1_v2 ~ v2)
12: mp_per_capita_flow(from = "V2", to = "E2", rate = foi2 ~ kappa2 * 
      beta * (tau * I + zeta * A)/N)
13: mp_per_capita_flow(from = "E2", to = "I2", rate = infect_symp2 ~ 
      sigma * mu)
14: mp_per_capita_flow(from = "E2", to = "A2", rate = infect_asymp2 ~ 
      sigma * (1 - mu))
15: mp_per_capita_flow(from = "A2", to = "R2", rate = asymp_recov2 ~ 
      gamma)
16: mp_per_capita_flow(from = "I2", to = "H2", rate = symp_hosp2 ~ 
      phi2 * xi2)
17: mp_per_capita_flow(from = "I2", to = "R2", rate = symp_recov2 ~ 
      phi2 * (1 - xi2))
18: mp_per_capita_flow(from = "H2", to = "R2", rate = hosp_recov2 ~ 
      omega2 * (1 - theta2))
19: mp_per_capita_flow(from = "H2", to = "C2", rate = hosp_icu2 ~ 
      omega2 * theta2)
20: mp_per_capita_flow(from = "C2", to = "R2", rate = icu_recov2 ~ 
      eta2 * (1 - lambda2))
21: mp_per_capita_flow(from = "C2", to = "D2", rate = icu_dead2 ~ 
      eta2 * lambda2)
22: mp_per_capita_flow(from = "V2", to = "V3", rate = v2_v3 ~ v3)
23: mp_per_capita_flow(from = "V3", to = "E3", rate = foi3 ~ kappa3 * 
      beta * (tau * I + zeta * A)/N)
24: mp_per_capita_flow(from = "E3", to = "I3", rate = infect_symp3 ~ 
      sigma * mu)
25: mp_per_capita_flow(from = "E3", to = "A2", rate = infect_asymp3 ~ 
      sigma * (1 - mu))
26: mp_per_capita_flow(from = "A3", to = "R3", rate = asymp_recov3 ~ 
      gamma)
27: mp_per_capita_flow(from = "I3", to = "H3", rate = symp_hosp3 ~ 
      phi3 * xi3)
28: mp_per_capita_flow(from = "I3", to = "R3", rate = symp_recov3 ~ 
      phi3 * (1 - xi3))
29: mp_per_capita_flow(from = "H3", to = "R3", rate = hosp_recov3 ~ 
      omega3 * (1 - theta3))
30: mp_per_capita_flow(from = "H3", to = "C3", rate = hosp_icu3 ~ 
      omega3 * theta3)
31: mp_per_capita_flow(from = "C3", to = "R3", rate = icu_recov3 ~ 
      eta3 * (1 - lambda3))
32: mp_per_capita_flow(from = "C3", to = "D3", rate = icu_dead3 ~

Piecewise Time Variation

beta_changepoints <- c(0, 10, 21, 55, 90)
beta_values <- c(5.10, 0.17, 0.63, 0.90, 0.83)
time_steps = 170
state_labels = c("S", "E", "A", "I", "R","H", "C", "D",
                  "S1", "E1", "A1", "I1", "R1","H1", "C1", "D1",
                  "V2", "E2", "A2", "I2", "R2","H2", "C2", "D2",
                  "V3", "E3", "A3", "I3", "R3","H3", "C3", "D3",
                 "cases"
                 )

expr = list(beta ~ time_var(beta_values, beta_changepoints))

# model specification with piece-wise transmission rates
piecewise_spec = searchid_spec |> 
    mp_tmb_insert(
      phase="during"
    , at=1L
    , expressions = expr
    , default = list(beta_values = log(beta_values))
    , integers = list(beta_changepoints = beta_changepoints)
    )
  
# transformed model specification
transformed_spec = mp_tmb_insert(
    model = piecewise_spec
  , phase = "before"
  , at = 1L
  , expressions = list(beta_values ~ exp(log_beta_values))
  , default = list(log_beta_values = rep(mean(log(beta_values)), length(beta_values)))
)

# create simulator object
transformed_spec_simulator = (transformed_spec |> 
                                mp_rk4() |> 
                                mp_simulator(time_steps = 170, outputs = c(state_labels))
                              )
(transformed_spec_simulator
  |> mp_trajectory()
  |> mutate(state = factor(matrix, state_labels))
  |>  ggplot()
 + geom_line(aes(time, value, colour = state))
  + geom_point(aes(time, value, colour = state), size = 0.5)
  + geom_vline(
    aes(xintercept = x),
    linetype = "dashed",
    alpha = 0.5,
    data = data.frame(x = beta_changepoints)
  )+
  labs(x = "Date (Dec 2021  - June 2022)", y = "Omicron Incidence", title = "SEARCH-ID Model Incidence Trajectory With macpan2", color = "")+

 facet_wrap(~ state, scales = "free")
 + theme_clean()
)

Set up the Optimizer

Now we can create an object that can be calibrated.

searchid_calibrator = mp_tmb_calibrator(
    spec = transformed_spec |> mp_rk4() 
  , data = observed_data
  , traj = "cases"  
  , par = c("log_beta_values", "gamma","mu","sigma",
            "lambda1","lambda2","lambda3",
            "E1", "A1", "I1", "R1","E2", "A2", "I2", "R2","E3", "A3", "I3", "R3")
  , tv = mp_rbf("log_beta_values", dimension = 1)
  , default = list(gamma = 1/14, sigma = 1/3.3, mu = 0.6, kappa1 = 1, kappa2 = 0.91, kappa3 = 0.3, 
                   tau = 0.799, zeta = 0.75)#, v2 = 0.2828, v3 = 0.1359)
)
# ,"phi1","phi2","phi3", "eta1","eta2","eta3","v2", "v3", "xi1","xi2","xi3", "omega1", "omega2","omega3","theta1","theta2","theta3",
mp_optimize(searchid_calibrator)

euler_coef <- (mp_tmb_coef(searchid_calibrator, conf.int=TRUE)
       |> backtrans()
)

plot_fit = function(cal_object) {
  fitted_data = mp_trajectory_sd(cal_object, conf.int=TRUE)
  fitted_data$dates <- seq.Date(from = as.Date("2021-12-01"), by = "day", length.out = nrow(fitted_data))
  fitted_data <- fitted_data[fitted_data$dates > "2021-12-14",]
  observed_data <- observed_data[observed_data$dates > "2021-12-14",]
  ggplot(observed_data, aes(x = dates, y = value, colour = "black"), na.rm = TRUE) +
    geom_line(size = 2) +
    geom_line(aes(x = dates, y = value,colour = "red"), data = fitted_data,  size = 1) +
    geom_ribbon(aes(x = dates, ymin = conf.low, ymax = conf.high), data = fitted_data, alpha = 0.2) +
    labs(x = "Date (Dec 2021  - June 2022)", y = "Omicron True Infections", title = "SEARCH-ID Model Fit With macpan2", color = "") +
    scale_color_manual(labels = c("true incidence", "macpan2 fit"),values = c("black","red")) +
    annotate("text", x = as.Date("2021-12-18"), y = 700, label = expression(beta[2] == 0.20),size = 6,angle = 90, hjust = 1, color = "black")+
  annotate("text", x = as.Date("2021-12-28"), y = 700, label = expression(beta[3] == 5.21),size = 6,angle = 90, hjust = 1,color = "black")+
  annotate("text", x = as.Date("2022-01-30"), y = 550, label = expression(beta[4] == 0.62),size = 6,angle = 0, hjust = 1, color = "black")+
  # annotate("text", x = as.Date("2022-02-05"), y = 3, label = "Alert Level 3",size = 5,angle = 10, hjust = 1, color = "black")+
  annotate("text", x = as.Date("2022-03-03"), y = 550, label = expression(beta[3] == 0.70),size = 6,angle = 0, hjust = 1, color = "black")+
  annotate("text", x = as.Date("2022-05-01"), y = 1500, label = expression(beta[0] == 0.82),size = 6, hjust = 1, color = "black")+
    theme_clean() +
    geom_vline(xintercept = as.Date("2022-03-18"), colour = "purple", linetype = 6, size = 1)  +
      # geom_vline(xintercept = as.Date("2022-04-10"), colour = "purple", linetype = 6, size = 2)  +
    geom_vline(xintercept = as.Date("2021-12-23"), colour = "gold4", linetype = 2, size = 1)  +
    geom_vline(xintercept = as.Date("2022-01-03"), colour = "gold4", linetype = 2, size = 1)  +
    geom_vline(xintercept = as.Date("2022-02-06"), colour = "gold4", linetype = 2, size = 1)  +
    geom_vline(xintercept = as.Date("2022-03-14"), colour = "gold4", linetype = 1, size = 1)  +
    annotate("text", x = as.Date("2022-03-05"), y = 2200, label = "Pre-Cancellation of Public \nHealth Emergency Declaration",size=5, hjust=1, color = "darkblue")+
    annotate("text", x = as.Date("2022-05-14"), y = 2200, label = "Post Cancellation of Public \nHealth Emergency Declaration",size=5, hjust=1,color = "darkblue")+
    theme(axis.text.x = element_text(size = 20, angle = 45, hjust = 1),
          axis.title.x = element_text(size = 20, color = "black", face = "bold"),
          axis.text.y = element_text(size = 20),
          axis.title.y = element_text(size = 20, color = "black", face = "bold"),
          plot.title = element_text(size = 18, face = "bold", color = "black", hjust = 0.5),
          legend.position = c(0.75, 0.35),
          legend.title = element_text(size = 20),
          legend.text = element_text(size = 15),
          legend.background = element_rect(color = NA),
          legend.margin = margin(0, 0, 0, 0),
          plot.background = element_blank()) +
          theme(plot.title = element_text(hjust = 0.5))
}
